# Midterm Pre‑Production Packet — MM/VI 9A Video Production (Fall 2025)

> **Project Title:** *Quiet Nerves*
> **Scene:** INT. LIBRARY — DAY
> **Director:** Zhonghuang “Tommy” He
> **Latest Update:** <!-- YYYY‑MM‑DD --> 2025-10-15
> **Target Runtime:** ~60 seconds
> **Shot Count:** 10–12 (max 15)

This packet gathers all deliverables requested for the MM/VI 9A midterm: revised script (≤2 pages), storyboards (10–12 shots), shot list, overhead(s), script breakdown, schedule, call sheet, continuity notes, gear list, risk & accessibility plan, and submission checklist.

